    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give Ofgem powers to force energy suppliers to release customers ",
        "additional_details": "The predecessors (here) also had issues with the energy company not relinquishing supply. The Ombudsman was powerless to ask the energy company to release me even as an involuntary customer. I am today, potentially being forced to line this company's pockets.",
        "background": "Give households the 'power' to choose which energy company supplies the home. I inherited my current provider. We had no contract but they will not release me to pursue my chosen provider. When newly renting a home, one is at the mercy of existing energy companies.",
